                            <additions>
                                <p>
                                    <locus from="1r" to="1r" scheme="folios"/>
                                    <note> Below the prayers in a cursive hand: <quote>Istud missale fecit scribi dominus gummundus pie memorie quondam capellanus domus sancti spiritus de propria pecunia anno domini mcdlxo <gap reason="editorial"/> plura bona fecit fieri</quote>.</note>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <locus from="1v" to="1v" scheme="folios"/>
                                    <note>Note dated 1524 on the confiscation of silver from Helgeandshuset on Gustav Vasa’s behalf by Paval Skolte, superintendent of the hospital in 1519-21 and 1523.</note>
                                </p>
                                <p>
                                    <locus from="8r" to="8r" scheme="folios"/>
                                    <note>Note in Swedish on a donation made by Hans Laurensson Klysieur (Hans Krokfooth) to the hospital, dated 1506.</note>
                                </p>
                            </additions>
                            <decoDesc>
                                <p>Main text in black ink, rubrics in red.</p>
                                <decoNote type="initials">
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="2r" to="7v" scheme="folios"/>: Simple inital KL in blue and red over 2-3 lines with flourishing in brown and red ink. <locus from="8v" to="8v" scheme="folios"/>: Chapter puzzle initial E over 3 lines in blue and red, counter space filled in with lines in brown ink. <locus from="8v" to="10v" scheme="folios"/>: plain initials over 2 lines alternating in blue and red.</p>
                                </decoNote>
                            </decoDesc>
